title: My Daily Phrase German - Week 1 Vocabulary List
description: This vocabulary list provides all words and phrases covered in both the basic daily podcasts and the bonus vocabulary from the weekly review podcast. It is in pdf format and is provided as a sample of the type of material included in the Premium Membership version of My Daily Phrase German.
